b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Bing Image Creator is best suited for free DALL E 3 access, casual users, quick images, beginners, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Deep Dream Generator, meanwhile, shines for artistic effects, style transfer, surreal art, creative experimentation, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2023, Bing Image Creator describes itself as \"Free DALL-E 3 powered image generator by Microsoft.\" Deep Dream Generator, established in 2015, positions itself as \"AI art generator known for surreal and psychedelic visual styles.\" With 8 years between them, Deep Dream Generator brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Bing Image Creator offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Bing Image Creator** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 4.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Deep Dream Generator is a poor choice — far from it. Deep Dream Generator excels in its own right, particularly for artistic effects and style transfer.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value completely free dall-e 3 access, go with Bing Image Creator. If unique artistic styles not found elsewhere matters more to you, Deep Dream Generator is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
